---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="Privacy and Policy" headerTitle="Privacy and Policy">
  <main>
    <section
      id="privacy-policy"
      class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 p-12 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-12"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
      >
        Privacy Policy
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">
        At Freedom Butchers, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy
        outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the
        measures we take to ensure it is protected.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Information We Collect
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-justify">
        We collect personal information to improve your experience. This
        includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-8 pl-6 space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>Name, email address, and phone number</li>
        <li>Order history and preferences</li>
        <li>Payment information (securely processed)</li>
        <li>Browsing data from cookies and analytics tools</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        How We Use Your Information
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        Your data is used to process orders, improve our services, and
        communicate important updates or offers. We do not sell or share your
        personal information with third parties, except as required by law.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Data Security
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data
        from unauthorized access or misuse. Our systems are regularly updated
        and monitored for potential vulnerabilities.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Your Rights
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-justify">You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-8 pl-6 space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>Access and correct your personal information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data, subject to legal obligations</li>
        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Policy Updates
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        We may update this policy as needed to reflect changes in our practices
        or the law. Any updates will be posted on this page.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Contact Us
      </h3>
      <p class="text-center text-lg">
        For questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us
        at <a
          href="mailto:contact@freedombutchers.com"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact@freedombutchers.com</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
